Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:10.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Scale Festival starts tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:12.35,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is really excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.66,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's our first festival in Akihabara, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.61,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Since the festival was approved,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,many guilds have been making \Nspecial items for the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.16,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:27.16,SignA,N,0000,0000,0000,,Licensed by the Round Table \NPrincess Figures (Wood Carved)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:27.16,SignB,N,0000,0000,0000,,Only 40 of Each Design! \N500 Gold
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:27.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just hearing there's a festival makes \Na lot of people want to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:30.04,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.09,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You've got quite a lot there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.84,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They won't even fit in my magic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:39.26,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Crescent Moon Alliance will \Nbe selling winter clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a fashion show, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:43.85,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:47.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It starts tomorrow, so we're \Ndoing the final touches today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.14,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:52.69,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Crescent Moon Burgers \Nwill be making their return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.62,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:57.47,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you be doing during the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:01.71,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going around and \Nenjoying all the different shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:02.70,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I will eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.95,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And eat some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:05.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And Akatsuki and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:08.87,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I didn't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What'll the girls be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:18.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please come as a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:24.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I have to invite Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.02,SignC,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All-You-Can-Eat Cake Buffet \N{\c&H3D0288&\fs20}Come as a couple, and get in free!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.69,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I've only made it this far because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:07.40,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.46,SignC,S,0000,0000,0000,,All-You-Can-Eat Cake Buffet \N{\c&H3D0288&\fs20}Come as a couple, and get in free!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:36.86,Title,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1470,1)}Swallow and Young Starling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Swallow and Young Starling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.61,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.85,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shutting yourself up in here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Handling the Round Table's paperwork, \Ninvestigating this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:50.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have a ton of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.40,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.39,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes and yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:00.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I ate two hours ago, and I \Ntook a fifteen-minute nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.76,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Here is what you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you had just sent a message, \NI would've come to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.61,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,So you say, but would you really have come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:18.25,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard you've been locked in here for ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.41,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to check on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How's the Scale Festival looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Karashin's going all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.74,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,He's really taken charge of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He does good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:34.50,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You should take a break \Nfor these next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:36.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,During the festival, it'll be pretty noisy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,so I probably won't be able to concentrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:48.51,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good chance for you to \Nbecome closer to your guildmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.01,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:54.03,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Log Horizon is one of the Round Table guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:57.18,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be out there, making the event fun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.80,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:01.90,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:06.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki and Minori are so cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.33,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,An Akatsuki doll that Akatsuki gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A voodoo doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:19.79,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, as long as I have my fantasies, \NI barely even need to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.86,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,They say that man does not live by bread alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:28.45,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,But with bread and fantasies, \Nyou can get over almost anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God almighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:36.31,SignA,H,0000,0000,0000,,You're just playing around, \Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:36.31,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,She's right... During the festival, \Nit'll be hard to do much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.76,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,When reports come in, \NI'll have to do some fancy footwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.32,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll end up waiting, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.93,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, nothing has happened in Minami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:46.93,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,M-My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You want a red bean bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:00.62,SignC,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\c&H1E7255&}Red Bean Buns
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Great weather today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like forever since I was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, red bean buns are expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:16.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:17.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:28.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I've had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's bean paste on your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, you've looked pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.59,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,M-My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do during the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll probably have to help with things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, do you like c-c-ca...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.32,SignC,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,All-You-Can-Eat Cake Buffet \N{\c&H3D0288&\fs20}Come as a couple, and get in free!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.32,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Voilà!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:18.01,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,So, about the Scale Festival tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.99,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go to this with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A cake buffet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.65,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You enjoy sweets, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,From the way he eats his red bean buns, \Nthat would seem to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly don't dislike them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If we go as a couple, it's free!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.40,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It's free! Totally free!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.31,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.56,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.16,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.41,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:56.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.08,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.33,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:05.03,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pre-festival dance tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.03,0:08:06.08,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come with...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.70,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:11.39,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going out with Shiroe tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.23,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not sure what to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:14.43,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.57,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,With Shiroe, the shut-in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:25.96,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I've seen him outside for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.46,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.85,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,A cake buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.40,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, eating cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.24,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.76,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you win this contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get two tickets to the Twilight Banquet \Nwith Princess Lenessia on the second day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:41.33,SignA,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Participants compete to see who can eat the most slices! \NThe top two teams advance to the final battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:47.04,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No one trusts Shiroe. They say they \Ndon't know what he's thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.09,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But he's actually really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.22,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad that they don't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.37,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I want them all to know more about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.60,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.00,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.73,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.06,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'll coordinate your outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:15.28,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Minori have to put pressure on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.17,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,My rival is a middle-schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:23.44,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he does normally treat me \Nlike a kid, this doesn't seem fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.97,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my lord's fault for treating me as a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.16,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.00,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.11,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,...because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:38.26,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord didn't judge me based \Non my appearance or level.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:43.51,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,He accepted me for who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:50.24,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord said he'd attend the buffet \Nwith both Minori and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.15,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But it's supposed to be a couple, \Nso we'll probably be alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.47,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.12,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,...a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.36,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.12,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.75,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,And what will I wear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.36,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting lively around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:13.80,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I have no cute clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.63,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.59,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll ask someone to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.23,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.06,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki needs my help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.34,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.06,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick something myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.06,SignD,A,0000,0000,0000,,Crafting Guild \NCouncil Office \N\NKnock First{\c&H1A32BF&}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.06,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to be expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.77,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.82,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The Council doesn't play favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.18,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your location is determined by lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.82,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,We must adhere to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.99,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're doing all that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.99,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.60,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,This place is like a business congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.42,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are these all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.20,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I asked everyone to submit them
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could check for any dangerous items.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:59.15,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a terrifying amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.51,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.39,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The People of the Land's \Nmerchants are also coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:09.63,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting the sense that the festival \Nis a lot bigger than it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.56,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The next few days are gonna be hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.47,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.20,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.52,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,This is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.49,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.99,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...require fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, of Log Horizon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And two others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.57,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask this of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if that's the case, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:55.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this will be difficult for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.46,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,What did she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.08,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It really is all couples...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.58,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.26,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad all three of us could get in together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.73,Default - flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What? All three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:17.59,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:21.12,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got permission from \NKanako, the organizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.87,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to eat twelve to enter \Nas a trio, but I think we can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.50,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.88,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win, and go to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.35,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.34,Default - flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:38.83,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't think \NI could've eaten here twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.61,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:45.11,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling? Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.57,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That's a wonderful kimono, Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare to see you in a kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.26,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:57.91,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A guild called Kimono Komachi made it for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:01.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gr—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It is not for graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It is for fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Gr—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's graceful, and really nice. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.86,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:13.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You look good, too, Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.11,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:19.86,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isuzu chose this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:24.71,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she took me to a bunch of stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.28,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come with us sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.69,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isuzu knows a lot about clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.75,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.11,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord! My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.50,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I have high hopes for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.09,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.70,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:47.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think I could eat four of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:55.22,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Here, enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,"Enjoy"? But those are whole cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little present from my guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.96,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Present?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.13,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.16,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.43,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Really, my lord? You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:24.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Serving my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Serving me? That's a whole cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.06,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.61,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair that you got to bring two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.31,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.97,Default - italics,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... Is that how this looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:40.83,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to show off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:42.50,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.57,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good... I'll get them both involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope his glasses break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.67,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I need to avoid making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.19,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Minimize damage and retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:50.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:52.85,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Am I supposed to eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:57.33,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.43,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it'll fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.25,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.18,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:15.53,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Try this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:18.69,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, it's good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:27.00,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather fight a dozen raid bosses at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.08,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.51,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:33.70,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.86,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.70,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.71,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:54.58,SignA,S,0000,0000,0000,,Café {\fs24}Kanako
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:51.12,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you had to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't eat them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go home and rest, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:00.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to see the rest of the \Nfestival, but I think I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.27,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... You two go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.86,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make a stop before going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.87,Default - italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dandelion barley tea is good for digestion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.98,Default - italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad I couldn't attend \Nthe Twilight Banquet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:24.21,Default - italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but Shiroe worked hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.23,Default - italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.14,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.64,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Three people eating twelve whole cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:43.44,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,How did she figure that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.82,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,A cake buffet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be there tomorrow. \NWhy not go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.02,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:55.74,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.32,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the information, Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:00.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.31,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many whole \Ncakes he'll end up eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:10.60,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,But all the girls love Soujirou,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:13.37,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,yet he still does well running his guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:19.12,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu or Chief Nyanta seem more \Nlike guild masters than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.97,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have the presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:27.19,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Henrietta's right, and this \Nwould be a good chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.51,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I should make time to spend with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:31.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The town is even more lively than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:50.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It is a festival, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,When we first arrived in this world, \NI never would've imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:01.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:03.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.14,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.52,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do you, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Dislike cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:17.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you not have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:22.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm sorry we didn't get to the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It was Minori who wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But was that cake okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like I was doing all the eating. \NDid you have any?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:44.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't there for the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:49.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to hold a conversation \Nwith you, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I have all sorts of things to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:01.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then give us something to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.37,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a little harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:10.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I didn't mean... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:12.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.77,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:34.78,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is this part of her lord-and-servant role playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:41.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.86,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.53,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.41,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.34,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.16,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:19.61,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.61,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:30.81,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:35.58,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.00,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:42.92,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Not fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.29,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:52.86,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.35,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:09.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.29,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.44,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:19.53,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,think I like Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:20.67,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just now figuring it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was obvious to the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.68,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's nice, and he's caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.44,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why you'd admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:36.42,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:38.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can tell! We're twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I admire him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.45,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You like him, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:45.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:51.11,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:52.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:53.82,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:02.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem... \NYou're just hurt, Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:09.46,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:11.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:16.82,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:20.20,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:21.34,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It just hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:25.56,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost anything, \Nand I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:30.99,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't done anything yet, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:32.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:34.78,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:09.37,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The girl simply admired him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:11.52,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to be like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:12.93,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,To follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:15.01,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,To stand behind him. That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.37,0:24:19.64,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't take long for those \Nfeelings to turn to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.28,0:24:22.34,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Minori is in love with Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:30.99,Title,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Student of the Mage
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.04,0:24:25.22,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Student of the Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.63,0:24:27.62,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,We will change the world.
